article.description: — Curt Lewis had 18 points and 10 rebounds as Eastern Kentucky routed Eastern Illinois 82-43 on Monday night.
article.headline: Lewis, Williams lead E. Kentucky over E. Illinois 82-43
article.linkText: Lewis, Williams lead E. Kentucky over E. Illinois 82-43
article.story: RICHMOND, Ky. -- — Curt Lewis had 18 points and 10 rebounds as Eastern Kentucky routed Eastern Illinois 82-43 on Monday night. Jannson Williams added 16 points, 10 rebounds and six blocks for Eastern Kentucky (5-1). Michael Moreno chipped in 15 points and Russhard Cruickshank had 10. Moreno posted seven rebounds and six steals. Sammy Friday IV had seven rebounds for the Panthers (1-4). Henry Abraham added six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
